        <mxCell id="sr3Lcem74erj5iztOOXT-7" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;This diagram illustrates the backend management and regulatory oversight functions of the banking system. It focuses on administrative integrity by &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;148&quot;&gt;including&lt;/b&gt; mandatory &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;168&quot;&gt;System Logging&lt;/code&gt; for sensitive operations such as &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;216&quot;&gt;Freeze/Unfreeze Customer Account&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;253&quot;&gt;Update Exchange Rate&lt;/code&gt;, ensuring a transparent audit trail. The model handles exceptional workflows via &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;355&quot;&gt;extend&lt;/b&gt; relationships, where an account application may be &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;413&quot;&gt;Deferred&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;425&quot;&gt;Rejected&lt;/code&gt; based on specific compliance criteria. Key actors include the &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;496&quot;&gt;Bank Admin&lt;/b&gt;, responsible for internal controls and platform maintenance, and the &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;576&quot;&gt;Auditor&lt;/b&gt;, who performs independent reviews of transaction histories and account information to &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;670&quot;&gt;Generate Audit Reports&lt;/code&gt; for financial compliance.&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="220" width="310" x="10" y="20" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="sr3Lcem74erj5iztOOXT-8" edge="1" parent="1" style="endArrow=none;html=1;rounded=0;entryX=0.021;entryY=0.341;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;entryPerimeter=0;" target="uc_manage_rates">
